Resource Profile: openIMIS Claim Administrator Practitioner

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-claim-administrator-practitioner Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISClaimAdministratorPractitioner

Defines a Practitioner for openIMIS which maps to a Claim Administrator.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: openIMIS Claim Administrator Practitioner Role, openIMIS Claim Response and openIMIS Claim
  • Examples for this Profile: Practitioner/Rushila-Dani-CA
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
